  <brief_title>BAY59-7939 in Atrial Fibrillation Once Daily (OD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>BAY 59-7939 (Factor Xa Inhibitor) Phase II Once Daily Dose Study in Patients With Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
