  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an exploratory investigation of safety, pharmacokinetic (PK) and pharmacodynamic (PD)
      effects of BAY59-7939 with multiple oral doses of 10 mg, 15 mg and 20 mg once daily (od) in
      Japanese subjects with non-valvular atrial fibrillation (originally described in Japanese).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
